Class GDimension

    public class GDimension

    This class is a double-precision version of the Dimension class in java.awt.

      • equals

        public boolean equals(Object obj)
        Tests whether two GDimension objects are equal. Because floating-point values are inexact, this method checks for equality by comparing the float values (rather than the float values) of the coordinates.
